  "title": "Accounts Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Accounts Executive</strong></p>\n<p>Handle full sets of accounts and daily accounting operations</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare quotations, delivery orders, invoices, and project documentation</li>\n  <li>Process payments, staff claims and payroll</li>\n  <li>Filing of GST, CPF and other statutory submissions</li>\n  <li>Handle work pass applications, renewals, and cancellations</li>\n  <li>Support ad-hoc finance, admin, and marketing assignments as required</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Accountancy, Business or a related discipline</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of relevant accounting experience</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in accounting software such as SQL, Xero, or QuickBooks</li>\n  <li>IT-savvy and comfortable working with digital platforms and systems</li>\n  <li>Strong communication, interpersonal, and client engagement skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>What We Offer</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Exposure to a wide range of industries and business functions</li>\n  <li>Flexible and friendly working environment</li>\n  <li>Growth and learning opportunities across accounting, compliance, and client service</li>\n</ul>",
